        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/elastic-email-sender\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2969646\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/elastic-email-sender\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2969646\" alt=\"Install Elastic Email Sender with ease! Just fill in a few details and let us help you send better emails.\"><\/a><p>Install Elastic Email Sender with ease! Just fill in a few details and let us help you send better emails.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/elastic-email-sender\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2969646\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/elastic-email-sender\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2969646\" alt=\"A visual representation of your campaign&#039;s results. If you would like to know more about your campaigns statistics, please go to the Reports screen on the Elastic Email dashboard.\"><\/a><p>A visual representation of your campaign's results. If you would like to know more about your campaigns statistics, please go to the Reports screen on the Elastic Email dashboard.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/elastic-email-sender\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2969646\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/elastic-email-sender\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2969646\" alt=\"Test the sending configuration easily.\"><\/a><p>Test the sending configuration easily.<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/elastic-email-sender\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2969646\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/elastic-email-sender\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2969646\" alt=\"Error log\"><\/a><p>Error log<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/helderlopesofficial\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/0e7579824b9e9c877ffb44209d522a4c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/0e7579824b9e9c877ffb44209d522a4c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/helderlopesofficial\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">helderlopesofficial<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 25, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Excellent plugin to setup Cloudways SMTP Elastic Mail<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">quick &amp; easy to set up<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span